\id GAL - Saveeŋ (Tuam dialect) NT -Papua New Guinea 2011 (web 2014)
\h Galesia
\toc1 Rau Tau Paulus Iboode Pa Yes Galesia
\toc2 Galesia
\toc3 Ga
\mt1 Rau Tau Paulus Iboode Pa Yes Galesia
\mt2 Galesia—Galatians
\c 1
\s1 Maaron tauu ta ighur Paulus pa uraat tooni
\p 
\v 1 Yau Paulus, mbaŋooŋa to Yesu Krisi, ta nabood rau tane. Uraat tau naghamghamu ne, tamtamon eta ighur ghau pani mako, ve lupuuŋ eta to taan tighur ghau pani mako. Yesu Krisi gha Taama Maaron tau ipaburigini pa mateegh na, yesuru ta tighur ghau pa uraat tane. \x * \xo 1:1 \xt Mbaŋ 9:15\x*
\p 
\v 2 Toŋvetaz tisov to Krisi tau tileep tomani ghau ne, yeŋa nibood rau tane pa yam lupuuŋ to Krisi tau aleep irau taan sirivu to Galesia na. \x * \xo 1:2 \xt Mbaŋ 16:1-6, 18:23\x*
\p 
\v 3 Poia to Tamaan Maaron ve Tiina toit Yesu Krisi izaa tsiam, ve tiŋgin gham aleep poia toman lolomim luuma.
\v 4 Krisi iyoki tauu gha imaat itaghon Tamaan Maaron loolo, leso ireu sosor toit, ve ipas ghiit pa saghati tapiri tau aazne igheen irau taan. \x * \xo 1:4 \xt Mk 10:45\x*
\m 
\v 5 Tauvene tapait Maaron eeza pa tapiri ve poia tooni ta aazne, ve taghon taghon gha ila. Onoon.
\s1 Vaaru poia eemon ighengheen
\p 
\v 6-7 Oyai, yau nagham ŋgar naol pa yam Galesia. Aghita. Ila uraat to Yesu Krisi ve poia tooni, Maaron ipoi gham amin le wa. Eemon yam rekia mon aghur murimim pani, ve aghe ataghon vaaru poia ite. Ve vaaru poia eemon ta ighengheen. Ite paam mako. Alooŋ. Tamtamon siriv tau tilepleep tomani gham na, yes titortoor vaaru poia to Krisi, ve tikaukau ŋgar tsiam. Zeran tawe, saveeŋ toozi isapir kat. \x * \xo 1:6-7 \xt Mbaŋ 15:1, 24; 2Kor 11:3+\x*
\m 
\v 8 Tauvene yam alooŋ zi sov. Alooŋ. Isaav ighe tamtamon eta, ma aŋela to sambam eta ivotia vaaru poia payam, ve saveeŋ tooni isapir pa vaaru poia tau muuŋ yei nivotia payam, ene aatyavyav to Maaron aat izaa tooni ve ivaghamunia. Yei paam, isaav ighe nigham tauvene, aatyavyav to Maaron aat izaa tsiei ve ivaghamun ghei.
\v 9 Tauvene saveeŋ tau nisavia gha alooŋa wa, tauta aazne nayoli muul. Isaav ighe tamtamon eta ivotia saveeŋ payam, ve saveeŋ tooni isapir pa vaaru poia tau muuŋ yam aghamu na, aatyavyav to Maaron aat izaa tooni ve ivaghamunia. \x * \xo 1:9 \xt Syg 22:18+\x*
\p 
\v 10 Yam agham ŋgar mindai? Saveeŋ tsiau tane, yau nasavia to nagham tamtamon lolozi poia payau? Mako. Yau nasavia leso Maaron loolo poia payau. Ve mindai? Yam aghe yau nazuari ghau to nagham tamtamon lolozi? Mako kat! Isaav ighe nagham tauvene, ene yau besooŋa to Krisi mako. \x * \xo 1:10 \xt 1Tes 2:4; Yems 4:4\x*
\s1 Yesu Krisi tauu ta ipaghazoŋai Paulus pa vaaru poia
\p 
\v 11 Yam toŋvetaz, yau naghe yam awatagh kat tauvene: Vaaru poia tau yau nasavia payam na, ene ivot ila to tamtamon eta to taan mako.
\v 12 Pasaa, yau naghamu ila to tamtamon eta mako. Ve tamtamon eta ipaghazoŋai ghau pani mako. Yesu Krisi tauu, ta ipaghazoŋai ghau pani. \x * \xo 1:12 \xt 1Kor 11:23; Ep 3:3\x*
\s1 Paulus ipaesia eez tau i itoor ŋgar tooni, ve Yesu Krisi ighuru imin mbaŋooŋa tooni
\p 
\v 13 Ŋgar tau muuŋ naghamghamu na, yam aat alooŋa wa. Saawe tau nataghon yes Yuda pa tutuuŋ ve suŋuuŋ toozi, naghur pataŋani tintiina izazaa to yes tau tileep ila lupuuŋ to Maaron na, ve nagham zi tileep saghat kat. Pasaa, naghe le nareu zi, ve napasov lupuuŋ toozi le isov kat. \x * \xo 1:13 \xt Mbaŋ 8:3, 26:9+; 1Tim 1:13\x*
\m 
\v 14 Saawe tana, yau nazuari ghau kat pa suŋuuŋ ve tutuuŋ to yei Yuda, le naliiv zetagŋa naol tau yeŋa tumbuuŋ eemon na. Pasaa, ŋgar tsiau iyaryaaŋ kat naghe le nataghon duduŋai tutuuŋ tisov to tibugŋa tau tigheen muuŋ ve ilam. \x * \xo 1:14 \xt Mbaŋ 22:3; Pil 3:6\x*
\p 
\v 15-16 Eemon, saawe tau tinaŋ ipoop ghau soone, Maaron isiigh ghau pataghaaŋ wa. Ve murei ra, i ipoi ghau namin le, itaghon tauu loolo ve poia tooni, ve itotoi Naatu payau, leso navotia vaaru pa yes tau Yuda mako na. Saawe tau gabua tana ivot payau, yau nala nail ŋeer eta to taan to ipaghazoŋai ŋgar tsiau ne mako. \x * \xo 1:15-16 \xt Yer 1:5; Mbaŋ 9:15; Ro 1:1\x*
\m 
\v 17 Ma rekia nazala Yerusalem pa ghitooŋ yes tau timin mbaŋooŋa to Krisi imin maata payau na mako. Malmalig nala naleep izi taan sirivu to Arabia. Naleep le isov, ra namuul nala pa nugh Damaskus.
\p 
\v 18 Ndaman tol isov, ra nazala Yerusalem pa ghitooŋ Petrus, ve yeiru nileep irau mboŋ saŋavul ve liim. \x * \xo 1:18 \xt Mbaŋ 9:26+\x*
\m 
\v 19 Saawe tana, naghita mbaŋooŋa siriv to Krisi mako. Naghita Yakobus tau Tiina toit taazi na mon. \x * \xo 1:19 \xt Mt 13:55\x*
\m 
\v 20 Saveeŋ tau naboode payam ne, ene karom mako. Ila Maaron maata, ene saveeŋ onoon.
\p 
\v 21 Yau naghita Petrus le isov, ra nala naleep izi taan sirivu to Siria ve Silisia. \x * \xo 1:21 \xt Mbaŋ 9:30\x*
\m 
\v 22 Saawe tana, lupuuŋ to Krisi tau tileep irau taan sirivu to Yudea na, tighita naghog mako.
\v 23 Tiloŋlooŋ varug mon tauvene: “Ŋeer tau muuŋ ighurghur pataŋani pa iit tamtamon tau taghur ila Krisi saveeŋ tooni, ve ireureu ghiit, tauta aazne ivovotia saveeŋ tana pa tamtamon.”
\v 24 Tauvene yes tilooŋ varug pa ŋgar tau Maaron igham payau na, ve tipait eeza pa tapiri ve poia tooni.
\c 2
\s1 Yes mbaŋooŋa tau tileep izi Yerusalem na, tiyok pa uraat to Paulus
\p 
\v 1 Ndaman saŋavul ve paaŋ isov, ra yeiru Banabas nizala muul pa Yerusalem. Saawe tana, nagham Titus ve yeŋa nila. \x * \xo 2:1 \xt Mbaŋ 11:27, 15:1+\x*
\m 
\v 2 Nazala sorok mako. Nataghon ŋgar tau Maaron ivotia payau, tauta nazala. Nila peria, ra yeŋa yes tau tamtamon tighit zi tighe yes timin daaba pa lupuuŋ to Krisi na, nila nilup ghei soghan, ve napaes pazi pa vaaru poia tau navovotia pa yes tau Yuda mako na. Pa naroi: Ighe murei tiburig ve tiyau avozi pa uraat tsiau, ene pale uraat tau naghamghamu na, ighur anooŋa mako.
\p 
\v 3 Ve aghita. Titus tau yeŋa nizala na, i Yuda mako. I to Grik. Eemon yes daaba tawe tizoornugh pa ravuuŋ waaro mako. \x * \xo 2:3 \xt Mbaŋ 16:3\x*
\m 
\v 4 Saawe tana, tamtamon siriv tau toŋvetaz tauu to Krisi mako na, tilam tizool ghei tighe tipadeu payei. Pasaa, yes tiwatagh: Yei nighur ila nighe: Iit tamtamon tau tapaak Krisi ve taleep ila tooni na, Krisi ipas ghiit pa eez to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ \f + \fr 2:4 \ft Zeran tau titaghon eez to tutuuŋ na, ŋgar toozi tauvene. Isaav ighe titaghon duduŋai tutuuŋ naol isov to Maaron, ene pale tiduduuŋ ila i maata. Ve ighe tisosor pa tutuuŋ tooni rigta, ene irau tiduduuŋ ila i maata mako.\f*
\m wa. Zeran tawe tighe tigham ghei nimin besooŋa sorok muul pa yes Yuda gabuazi ve tutuuŋ toozi. \x * \xo 2:4 \xt Mbaŋ 15:24; Pil 3:2+\x*
\m 
\v 5 Eemon yei niyooz ariaaŋ, ve nilooŋ aliŋazi rigta mako. Pasaa, nighe le saveeŋ onoon to vaaru poia igheen duduuŋ pa yam tau Yuda mako na.
\p 
\v 6 Tauvene yau napaesia vaaru poia tau navovotia na pa yes daaba tau tiŋginŋgin lupuuŋ to Krisi, ve tiyok pani mon. Tirere pani mako, ve tiseeŋga pa saveeŋ ite paam mako. Mako kat. Daaba tawe, tamtamon titandagh pazi tighe ezazi tintiina. Ve isaav ighe ezazi tintiina, ma lezi ezazi mako, ene yau nagham ŋgar pa gabua tauvene mako. Pasaa, Maaron paam igham ŋgar pa tamtamon ezazi mako. \x * \xo 2:6 \xt Mbaŋ 10:34; Ep 6:9\x*
\p 
\v 7 Yes daaba tana tighilaal ghau tighe: Maaron inumeer ghau, ve ighur uraat ila nimag ighe navotia vaaru poia pa yes tau Yuda mako na, raraate imin ighur uraat to votiaaŋ vaaru poia pa yes Yuda ila Petrus niima. \x * \xo 2:7 \xt Mbaŋ 22:21; Ro 11:13+\x*
\m 
\v 8 Pasaa, Maaron ighur ghau namin mbaŋooŋa pa yes tau Yuda mako na, ve ipapalot ghau pa uraat tau naghamghamu ila sosozi, raraate imin ighur Petrus imin mbaŋooŋa pa yes Yuda, ve ipapaloti pa uraat tau ighamghamu ila sosozi.
\v 9 Tauvene Yakobus, Petrus, ve Yoan, tau tamtamon tighit zi tighe timuŋmuuŋ pa uraat to Krisi na, yes tighilaal tighe: Maaron ighur poia tooni izaa tsiau, ve ighur uraat tane ila nimag. Ve lolozi poia pa yeiru Banabas uraat tsiei, ve tighita tighe yeŋa uraat tsiei eemon. Tauvene yeŋa nivataki nimamai, ve nimbu saveeŋ nighe yeiru Banabas aat nila nigham uraat ila yes tau Yuda mako na sosozi, ve yes tigham uraat pa yes Yuda.
\p 
\v 10 Gabua eemon tau tisaav payei tighe nighamu, ene vene: Yei aat matamai iŋgal tamtamon toozi tau mbolaaŋ igham zi na, ve niyambaar lezi uleeŋ siriv. Yau nalooŋ saveeŋ toozi tawe, ve nayok pani mon. Pasaa, muuŋ ve ilam, ŋgar tsiau iyaryaaŋ naghe nagham tauvene. \x * \xo 2:10 \xt Mbaŋ 11:29+; Ro 15:25; 2Kor 8:1+\x*
\s1 Paulus iyaon Petrus pa karom tooni
\p 
\v 11 Saawe tau Petrus izilam nugh Antiok, i igham ŋgar tau iduduuŋ mako. Tauvene yau nasaav duduuŋ ila maata, ve nayaoni.
\v 12 Pasaa, muuŋ, i yesŋa yes tau Yuda mako na, tiluplup zi pa ghanghaniiŋ. Eemon saawe tau Yakobus imbaaŋ zeetŋa siriv tila tivot toozi, Petrus imoghaagh pa yes tau Yuda mako na, ve yesŋa tilup zi muul mako. Pasaa, iroi pa yes tau tiyooz ariaaŋ pa tutuuŋ to Mose ve ŋgar to ravuuŋ tamtamon warozi. \x * \xo 2:12 \xt Mbaŋ 11:3\x*
\m 
\v 13 Ve i zigani mako. Yuda siriv tau tighur ila to Yesu na, tipaak Petrus pa karom tooni. Ve Banabas paam, tikau ŋgar tooni le itaghon zi pa karom toozi tawe.
\p 
\v 14 Yau naghita ŋgar toozi tawe isapir kat pa saveeŋ onoon to vaaru poia. Tauvene nasaav kat pa Petrus ila eval tiina matazi naghe: “Yo Yuda. Eemon yo upul Yuda gabuazi ve tutuuŋ toozi, ve uleep imin yes tau Yuda mako na. Mindai ta aazne utoor ŋgar tsio muul ve ughe utaghon Yuda gabuazi? Ŋgar tau ughamu na, ene pale igham yes tau Yuda mako na matazi iŋgal tighe yes aat titaghon yes Yuda gabuazi ve tutuuŋ toozi.” \x * \xo 2:14 \xt 1Tim 5:20\x*
\s1 Tamtamon tau ighe ighur ila to Yesu, ene i iduduuŋ ila Maaron maata
\p 
\v 15 Onoon, yes nugh nugh tau tikankaan pa Maaron na, timamalaaŋ pa tutuuŋ tooni irau saawe. Ve iit tau siŋ to Yuda duduuŋ ne, taghamgham tauvene mako.
\v 16 Eemon iit tawatagh: Ŋgar to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ, ene irau igham tamtamon eta iduduuŋ ila Maaron maata ne mako. Ghuruuŋ ila toit tau iŋarui Yesu Krisi, tauta imin eez pait gha taduduuŋ ila Maaron maata. Puughu tane ta iit taghur ila to Yesu Krisi, leso igham ghiit taduduuŋ ila Maaron maata. Ve eez to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ, ene tanumeera muul mako. Pasaa, tamtamon eta irau itaghon duduŋai tutuuŋ to Maaron, ve ighamu iduduuŋ ila Maaron maata ne mako. \x * \xo 2:16 \xt Mbaŋ 13:38+; Ro 3:20, 28; Ga 3:11\x*
\p 
\v 17 Tauta iit tazuari ghiit taghe le taghur ila to Yesu Krisi ve taleep tuŋia ila tooni. Leso i igham ghiit taduduuŋ ila Maaron maata. Onoon, saawe siriv, iit tamalaaŋ pa Maaron tutuuŋ tooni. Eemon pale tasaav mindai? Yesu Krisi imin puughu pa sosor toit tawe? Mako kat! \x * \xo 2:17 \xt Ga 5:16+\x*
\m 
\v 18 Ve aghita. Eez to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ, yau napaghazoŋaini naghe ene isov wa. Isaav ighe natoor ŋgar tsiau ve napayooz eez tawe muul, ene aat namalaaŋ pa Maaron ŋgar tooni. \x * \xo 2:18 \xt Ro 10:4\x*
\p 
\v 19 Tauvene eez to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ, yau napuli wa. Pasaa, saawe tau Krisi ibaad sosor tsiau atuya izala ai pambarooŋ itaghon saveeŋ to tutuuŋ, ene imin yau paam namaat tomania. Tauta aazne, naleep ila tutuuŋ saamba muul mako, ve nagham lepoogh paaghu ila to Maaron, ve nabesbees pani.
\v 20 Tauvene lepoogh tsiau tau aazne naghamu izi taan, ene taug naŋgini muul mako. Krisi tau ilepleep ila lolog ne, tauta iŋgin lepoogh tsiau. Tauvene yau naghur ila to Maaron Naatu tau ighur loolo payau kat, ve ipul tauu gha imaat payau. Ghuruuŋ ila tsiau tane, tauta aazne ighamgham pooz payau pa lepoghag to taan. \x * \xo 2:20 \xt Ro 6:6, 11, 7:6; 2Kor 5:15\x*
\m 
\v 21 Poia to Maaron tau izazaa toit ila uraat to Yesu Krisi na, irau matag veleghini imin kaut sorok ne mako. Isaav ighe ŋgar to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ irau igham ghiit taduduuŋ ila Maaron maata, ene Krisi imaat sorok. \x * \xo 2:21 \xt Hib 7:11\x*
\c 3
\s1 Yes Galesia tigham Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ ila eez to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ mako
\p 
\v 1 Aa yam kankanooŋa to Galesia, sei ikau ŋgar tsiam? Aazne, avaghamgham imin yes tau mura tivaghamun zi na! Saawe tau nileep tomani gham, yei nipaghazoŋai gham pa Yesu Krisi, le imin ta taumim aleep, ve aghita tiravu izala ai pambarooŋ. \x * \xo 3:1 \xt 1Kor 1:23; Ga 5:7\x*
\m 
\v 2 Aiyo, naghe naghason gham pa gabua ee. Yam agham Maaron Avuvu itaghon saa eez? Eez to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ, ma eez to alooŋ vaaru poia ve aghur ila? \x * \xo 3:2 \xt Mbaŋ 2:38; Ro 10:16+; Ep 1:13\x*
\m 
\v 3 Yam aat lemim ŋgar mako taa? Papazoge, Maaron Avuvu ipaburigin gham gha agham lepoogh poia ila tooni. Puughu mindai ta aazne aghe apasov uraat tooni ila taumim tapirimim?
\v 4 Gabua naol tau muuŋ ivotvot payam na, ene ivot payam sorok? Mako! \x * \xo 3:4 \xt 1Kor 15:2; 2Yo 8\x*
\p 
\v 5 Ve puughu mindai ta Maaron irei Avuvu payam, ve ighamgham gabua ŋgeretazi ila sosomim? Yam ataghon duduŋai tutuuŋ tooni, ta ighamgham tauvene payam ne? Mako. Yam alooŋ vaaru poia mon, ve aghur ila.
\s1 Abaram itotoi ghiit pa eez to ghuruuŋ ila
\p 
\v 6 Matamim iŋgal imuul ila pa Abaram. Maaron aliiŋa tau tiboode na, isaav tauvene:
\q2 “Abaram ighur ila to Maaron, tauta Maaron ighita ighe i ŋeer duduuŋa.” \x * \xo 3:6 \xt Gnp 15:6; Ro 4:3\x*
\m 
\v 7 Tauvene yam irau awatagh aghe yes tau titaghon eez to ghuruuŋ ila, tauta timin Abaram natŋa. \x * \xo 3:7 \xt Yo 8:39; Ro 4:11+\x*
\m 
\v 8 Maaron iwataghi wa: Murei, nugh nugh tau Yuda mako na, pale tighur ila vaaru poia, ve ghuruuŋ ila toozi tana igham zi tiduduuŋ ila i maata. Pasaa, Maaron aliiŋa tau tiboode na isaav tauvene: Muuŋ kat, Maaron ivotia vaaru poia pa Abaram ighe:
\q2 “Yo pale umin eez pa nughmariŋ to taan, leso poia tsiau izaa toozi.” \x * \xo 3:8 \xt Gnp 12:3, 18:18, 22:18\x*
\m 
\v 9 Tauvene tamtamon tisov tau tighur ila to Krisi na, poia to Maaron aat izaa toozi, imin muuŋ Abaram ighur ila ve poia to Maaron izaa tooni. \x * \xo 3:9 \xt Ro 4:16\x*
\s1 Eez to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ, i le pataŋani
\p 
\v 10 Yes tau tinumeer tighe ŋgar to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ pale imin eez pazi to tiduduuŋ ila Maaron maata, ene pale aatyavyav to Maaron izaa toozi ve ivaghamun zi. Saveeŋa tiboode pataghaaŋ wa:
\q2 “Saveeŋ naol tau tiboode ila rau to tutuuŋ na, yam aat matamim kisin zi ve ataghoniir zi le tisov. Ve sei tau ighe itaghon suvinia mako, ene pale aatyavyav to Maaron izaa tooni, ve ivaghamunia.” \x * \xo 3:10 \xt Lo 27:26\x*
\m 
\v 11 Tauvene tutuuŋ irau imin eez pa tamtamon eta to iduduuŋ ila Maaron maata mako. Ene igheen mataghare wa. Pasaa, Maaron aliiŋa tau tiboode ila rau na, isaav tauvene:
\q2 “Tamtamon tau ighe ighur ila, ene aat iduduuŋ ila Maaron maata, ve igham lepoogh poia ila tooni.” \x * \xo 3:11 \xt Hab 2:4; Ro 1:17; Ga 2:16; Hib 10:38\x*
\m 
\v 12 Eemon eez to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ, ene ŋgara ite pa eez to ghuruuŋ ila. Pasaa, eez to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ, ene vene:
\q2 “Tamtamon tau ighe itaghoniir tutuuŋ tisov, ene aat ileep poia.” \x * \xo 3:12 \xt Wkp 18:5; Ro 10:5\x*
\m 
\v 13 Tauvene eez to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ, ene igham pataŋani pait. Pa ighe tataghon duduŋai tutuuŋ mako, ene pale aatyavyav to Maaron izaa toit ve ivaghamun ghiit. Eemon Yesu igham niaan gha ibaad aatyavyav to Maaron izala ai pambarooŋ. Tauta igham mulin ghiit pa pataŋani tawe. Saveeŋa igheen pataghaaŋ wa:
\q2 “Ŋeer tau ighe tiravu ve ituuk ila ai, ene aatyavyav to Maaron igheen izaa tooni.” \x * \xo 3:13 \xt Lo 21:23; Ro 8:3; 2Kor 5:21\x*
\m 
\v 14 Krisi igham tauvene, leso poia to Maaron tau muuŋ izaa to Abaram na, izaa to yes tau Yuda mako na paam. Tauta aazne, iit tau taghur ila to Krisi na, tagham Maaron Avuvu itaghon saveeŋ mbuaaŋ tooni. \x * \xo 3:14 \xt Yo 7:38+; Ro 4:16\x*
\s1 Tutuuŋ to Maaron irau ireu saveeŋ mbuaaŋ tooni mako
\p 
\v 15 Yam toŋvetaz, yau naghe nagham saveeŋ palelaaŋ pa ŋgar tau monmon iit tamtamon taghamghamu ne. Isaav ighe tambu saveeŋ eta ve tapariaaŋa le iyaryaaŋ kat, ene murei tamtamon ite paam irau ireua, ma iseeŋga pa saveeŋ ite paam mako. Pasaa, saveeŋ mbuaaŋ tana iyaryaaŋ wa.
\v 16 Aiyo, mataan iŋgal saveeŋ tau muuŋ Maaron imbua tomania Abaram ve paaghu tooni. Saveeŋ tawe iŋarui Abaram paaghu tooni tisov mako. Iŋarui ŋeer eemon, ene Krisi. \x * \xo 3:16 \xt Gnp 12:7, 22:18, 24:7\x*
\m 
\v 17 Saveeŋ tsiau tane, puughu tauvene: Maaron imbu saveeŋ tomania Abaram, ve ipariaaŋa le iyaryaaŋ kat, ve ndaman ndiŋndiŋ paaŋ, tamoot ee, saŋavul (430) ilam ila, ra igham tutuuŋ pa yes Israela. Tauvene tutuuŋ tawe irau ireu saveeŋ mbuaaŋ tau muuŋ Maaron imbua ne mako. Pasaa, tutuuŋ ivot murei. \x * \xo 3:17 \xt Igham 12:40+\x*
\p 
\v 18 Lepoogh poia tau Maaron ighe igham pa tamtamon tooni na, imin ta ŋgar to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ irau imin eez pait to taghamu, kanaŋ taghamu ila eez tana, ve saveeŋ mbuaaŋ ileple. Eemon mako. Pasaa, Maaron imbu saveeŋ pa Abaram ighe i pale igham lepoogh poia tawe pani sorok. \x * \xo 3:18 \xt Ro 4:13, 11:6\x*
\s1 Puughu tau Maaron igham tutuuŋ pait
\p 
\v 19 Ighe vene, puughu mindai ta Maaron imbu saveeŋ le isov, ra izi gha igham tutuuŋ pa yes Israela? I igham tutuuŋ pa tamtamon to ipaburigin ŋgar toozi, leso tighilaal sosor toozi. Ve i ighe tutuuŋ tawe iyooz ariaaŋ le irau Abaram paaghu tooni tau i imbu saveeŋ pani na ilam ivot. Tutuuŋ tana, yes aŋela tigham pa Mose, ra i aana isakia ila pa yes Israela. Pasaa, i ta iyooz bodbodaaŋ pa Maaron ve yes Israela. \x * \xo 3:19 \xt Yo 1:17; Mbaŋ 7:38; Ro 5:20, 7:7\x*
\m 
\v 20 Eemon saawe tau Maaron imbu saveeŋ tomania Abaram, tamtamon eta, ma aŋela eta ileep bodbodaaŋ pa Maaron ve Abaram, ve isakia Maaron aliiŋa ila pa Abaram ne mako. Abaram ilooŋ saveeŋ ila Maaron tauu aavo. Pasaa, Maaron zigani ta ileep, ve isavia.
\p 
\v 21 Ma mindai? Saveeŋ mbuaaŋ to Maaron iparav tomania tutuuŋ tooni? Mako kat! Imin ta tutuuŋ eta irau imin eez pait to tagham lepoogh poia ila to Maaron, kanaŋ ŋgar to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ irau igham ghiit taduduuŋ ila Maaron maata.
\v 22 Eemon mako. Pasaa, Maaron aliiŋa tau tiboode na, isaav ghazooŋa tauvene: Ŋgar saghati ikau iit tasov, le tamin yes tau tileep ila ruum to yavyavuuŋ loolo. Saveeŋ tane ipaghazoŋai ghiit pa sosor toit. Leso taghur ila to Yesu Krisi, ve ghuruuŋ ila toit imin eez pait to taghita saveeŋ mbuaaŋ to Maaron anooŋa. \x * \xo 3:22 \xt Mbo 14:3; Ro 3:9+\x*
\p 
\v 23 Muuŋ, saawe tau taleep ila tutuuŋ saamba, lepoogh toit imin yes tau tileep ila ruum to yavyavuuŋ loolo. Pasaa, tutuuŋ iŋgin ghiit pa gabua naol isov. Taleep tauvene le Maaron ipaghazoŋai eez to ghuruuŋ ila ivot ighazooŋ. \x * \xo 3:23 \xt Ga 4:3; Hib 9:10\x*
\m 
\v 24 Agham ŋgar pa yes besooŋa tau tiŋgin geegeu ve tipaduduuŋ zi le timin zolman. \f + \fr 3:24 \ft Yes Grika lezi besooŋa siriv tau tiŋginŋgin natuzŋa. Yes tigham payamyam pa yes geegeu, ve murei tipaduduuŋ zi pa ŋgar le timin zolman. Mako tipul zi, ve geegeu tawe tiŋgin tauzi.\f*
\m Muuŋ, iit taleep ila tutuuŋ saamba, ve tutuuŋ iŋgin ghiit imin yes besooŋa tawe le Krisi ilam ivot. Leso igherev ghiit tala to Krisi, ve taghur ila tooni, ve i igham ghiit taduduuŋ ila Maaron maata. \x * \xo 3:24 \xt Mbaŋ 13:39\x*
\m 
\v 25 Ve aazne, eez to ghuruuŋ ila ivot ighazooŋ wa. Tauta taleep ila tutuuŋ saamba muul mako, ve tutuuŋ imin paduduŋaaŋ pait muul mako. \x * \xo 3:25 \xt Ro 7:6, 10:4; Kol 2:16+; Hib 8:13\x*
\s1 Yes tau tighur ila to Krisi na timin Maaron natŋa
\p 
\v 26 Yam asov tau ghuruuŋ ila tsiam isaghav Yesu Krisi na, Maaron natŋa yam. \x * \xo 3:26 \xt Yo 1:12; Ro 8:14+\x*
\m 
\v 27 Pasaa, yam tamtamon tau agham yaa gha amin Krisi le na, asov agham ŋgar to Krisi imin lemim wa, imin anonogh gham pa nonoghiiŋa paaghu. \x * \xo 3:27 \xt Ro 13:14; Kol 3:12\x*
\m 
\v 28 Ve yam asov raratemim ila Maaron maata. Isaav ighe yam Yuda, ma Yuda mako, ma yam besooŋa sorok, ma yam besooŋa mako ve aŋgin taumim, ma yam zilivaa, ma zitamoot, gabua naol tauvene, iit tagham ŋgar pani sov. Pasaa, yam aleep ila to Yesu Krisi, ve i ilup gham asov amin eemon wa. \x * \xo 3:28 \xt Yo 10:16; Ro 10:12+; 1Kor 12:13; Kol 3:11\x*
\m 
\v 29 Tauvene aazne, yam amin Krisi le wa. Ve amin Abaram paaghu tooni paam. Tauta ezamim pa ghamuuŋ lepoogh poia ila to Maaron, itaghon saveeŋ mbuaaŋ tau muuŋ i imbua tomania Abaram na. \x * \xo 3:29 \xt Gnp 21:12; Ro 9:7+\x*
\c 4
\s1 Iit tamin besooŋa pa tutuuŋ muul mako
\p 
\v 1-2 Saveeŋ tsiau tane, puughu tauvene: Isaav ighe tamtamon eta eeza pa ŋginiiŋ gabua naol isov to taama, ene irau iŋginiir gabua tana rekia mako. Saawe tau i kukua, taghita taghe lepoogh tooni, ene iliiv yes besooŋa to taama mako. Pasaa, i ileep ila besooŋa siriv sambazi, ve tiŋgini tomania gabua tooni tawe. Ve i aat ilepleep tauvene le tizaa pa saawe tau taama ighuru na, mako igham gabua tooni tana, ve tauu iŋgin zi.
\v 3 Yei Yuda tauvene paam. Muuŋ, nileep imin yes geegeu tau ŋgarig gha tighamgham ŋgar. Saawe tana, nibesbees pa tutuuŋ naol tau tisavia gabua to taan. \f + \fr 4:3 \ft Eez ite to tatoor ziiri tane, ene vene: “Saawe tana, taleep imin besooŋa sorok pa avuvu sasaghati tau tiŋgin gabua siriv to sambam ve taan.”\f* \x * \xo 4:3 \xt Ga 3:23\x*
\m 
\v 4 Nileep tauvene le nizaa pa saawe duduuŋ tau Maaron ighuru na, ra imbaaŋ tauu Naatu izilam taan. Livaa ee to taan ipoopa. Ve i ileep ila tutuuŋ saamba, ve itaghon katin tutuuŋ le isov. \x * \xo 4:4 \xt Mt 5:17; Yo 1:14\x*
\m 
\v 5 I ilam to igham mulin yei tau nileep ila tutuuŋ saamba. Leso nimin besooŋa sorok pa tutuuŋ muul sov, ve nimin Maaron natŋa. \x * \xo 4:5 \xt Yo 1:12; Ro 8:14+; Ga 3:13; 1Pe 1:18+\x*
\p 
\v 6 Ve yam paam, amin Maaron natŋa wa. Tauta Maaron imbaaŋ Naatu Avuvu ila lolomim. Avuvu tawe igham ghiit tapoipoi Maaron taghe: “Abba, tamaŋ” \f + \fr 4:6 \ft Yes geegeu to Israel tiwatwaat tamazŋa ila tauzi aliŋazi tighe ‘Abba’, imin iit taghe ‘tamaŋ’ o ‘ama’.\f*
\m 
\v 7 Tauvene aazne, yam amin besooŋa sorok muul mako. Pasaa, Maaron igham gham amin i tauu natŋa wa. Ve isaav ighe i natŋa yam, ene ezamim pa ghamuuŋ lepoogh poia ila tooni. \x * \xo 4:7 \xt Ro 8:17; Ga 3:29\x*
\s1 Paulus loolo ibubu pa yes Galesia
\p 
\v 8 Muuŋ, yam awatagh Maaron mako. Saawe tana, yam amin besooŋa sorok pa gabua soroksorok naol tau Maaron tauu mako. \x * \xo 4:8 \xt 1Kor 8:4, 12:2\x*
\m 
\v 9 Eemon aazne, yam awatagh Maaron wa. Aiss, nasaav vene sov. Maaron ta iwatagh gham, ve igham gham amin le wa. Tauvene puughu mindai ta aazne, yam aghur murimim pani, ve aghe amuul pa gabuamim muŋgaana, ve ataghon tutuuŋ naol to taan tau lezi tapirizi irau to tiuul gham mako na? \f + \fr 4:9 \ft Eez ite to tatoor ziiri tane, ene vene: “Tauvene puughu mindai ta aazne, yam aghur murimim pani, ve aghe amuul pa gabuamim muŋgaana, ve amin besooŋa pa avuvu siriv tau lezi tapirizi irau to tiuul gham mako na?” \f*
\v 10 Aazne, yam matamim iŋgalŋgal saawe tau kaiyo izaa paaghu, ve saawe to ndaman paaghu, ve saawe siriv ta aghur zi timin saawe to suŋuuŋ itaghon ŋgar to yes Yuda. \x * \xo 4:10 \xt Kol 2:16, 20; Hib 7:18\x*
\m 
\v 11 Tauta agham ghau lolog ibubu pa uraat tiina tau naghamu ila sosomim na. Pale ighur anooŋa, ma imin kaut sorok?
\s1 Paulus itaŋ rarai yes Galesia
\p 
\v 12-13 Yam toŋvetaz, aghita. Yau napul eez to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ, ve nataghon yam tau Yuda mako na pa gabuamim. Tauvene aazne, nataŋ rarai gham naghe atoor ŋgar tsiam, ve amuul alam ataghon ghau pa ŋgar tau yau naghamghamu ne. Saveeŋ tsiau tane, nasavia pasaa, naghe yam agham sosor payau, ene mako. Yam awatagh: Saawe imin maata tau nalat navotia vaaru poia payam, yau namorooŋ, tauta nazalat naleep tomani gham. \x * \xo 4:12-13 \xt 1Kor 2:3\x*
\m 
\v 14 Moroghooŋ tsiau tana igham pataŋani tiina payam. Eemon matamim veleghin ghau, ma azor ghau mako. Yam apakur ghau kat, imin yau aŋela eta to Maaron, ma Yesu Krisi tauu.
\v 15 Saawe tana, yam tintinmim kat pa poia to Maaron tau izaa tsiam. Eemon aazne, tintinmim muul mako. Ene mindai? Onoon kat, yau nasaav payam: Saawe tana, lolomim pa uleeŋ ghau kat. Irau aŋguruut gabua eta payau mako. Imin ta yam irau auul ghau pa matamim, kanaŋ apasu ve agham payau!
\v 16 Mindai, yau nasavia saveeŋ onoon payam, tauta aghe naghur koi payam?
\p 
\v 17 Zeran tau tizuari zi pa ghamuuŋ lolomim na, ŋgar toozi poia mako. Yes tighe tigham gham amoghaagh payau, leso ataghon zi pa ŋgar toozi.
\v 18 Saawe isov, isaav ighe tazuari ghiit pa ghamuuŋ ŋgar popoia, ene poia. Tauvene saawe tau naleep tomani gham mako, yam aat matamim kisin ŋgar poia ve ataghoni.
\v 19 O natugŋa, ŋgar tau aghamu na, ene igham pataŋani tiina payau muul imin zilivaa tau apozi iyavyav pa popaaŋ. Ve yau aat nabaad pataŋani tane le irau ŋgar to Krisi ivot imin tiina ila lolomim. \x * \xo 4:19 \xt Ro 8:29; 1Kor 4:15\x*
\m 
\v 20 Oyai, pale nagham mindai payam? Aazne naleep malau payam. Imin ta itiŋa taleep, kanaŋ alooŋ saveeŋ duduuŋ ila avog ve nasavia saveeŋ popoia siriv to napaghazoŋai ŋgar tsiam.
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to Agar gha Sara
\p 
\v 21 Yam tau aghe aleep ila tutuuŋ saamba na, asaav payau lak. Yam alooŋ saveeŋ to tutuuŋ, ma mako?
\v 22 Pa Maaron aliiŋa tau tiboode na isaav tauvene: Abaram natŋa ru. Ee, ivot ila to Agar, i livaa tau besooŋa sorok na. Ve ite ivot ila to azaawa Sara, tau ruum tauu na. \x * \xo 4:22 \xt Gnp 16:15, 21:2\x*
\m 
\v 23 Besooŋa livaa naatu, i ivot itaghon eez to iit tamtamon to taan. Ve livaa tau ruum tauu na naatu, i ivot itaghon saveeŋ mbuaaŋ to Maaron. \x * \xo 4:23 \xt Gnp 17:16, 18:10+; Ro 9:7+; Hib 11:11\x*
\p 
\v 24 Saveeŋ tane, ene imin saveeŋ palelaaŋ. Pasaa, zilivaa ru tawe titotoi ghiit pa eez ru tau Maaron ighuru pa tamtamon. Agar, i imin eez to tutuuŋ tau ivot izi loloz Sinai. Yes tau titaghon eez tawe na timin besooŋa sorok.
\v 25 Loloz Sinai, ene igheen taan sirivu to Arabia. Agar imin loloz tawe ve nugh Yerusalem tau aazne igheen izi taan ne. Pasaa, nugh tawe tamtamona timin besooŋa sorok pa tutuuŋ.
\v 26 Eemon Yerusalem tauu ta igheen izi sambam na, tamtamona timin besooŋa mako. Yes nugh tauŋa. Yerusalem tawe, ta imin iit tinaan. \x * \xo 4:26 \xt Ro 8:15; Hib 12:22; Syg 21:2, 10\x*
\m 
\v 27 Pasaa, Maaron aliiŋa tau tiboode na isaav ighe:
\q2 “Yo livaa tau upoop mako na, tintinim!
\q2 Yo livaa tau uyamaan yavyavuuŋ pa popaaŋ soone na, lolom poia ve aliŋam izaa!
\q2 Pa livaa tau azaawa ighur muuri pani na, pale natŋa katini ve tiliiv livaa tau i le azaawa na natŋa.” \f + \fr 4:27 \ft Muuŋ, lupuuŋ to yes Israela tomania Maaron poia. Eemon yes eval mako. Saawe tana, yes tileep imin livaa tau i le azaawa. Eemon saawe naol, tizoor Maaron aliiŋa. Tauvene murei, i ighur muuri pazi, ve ipul zi tila yes Babilona ve nugh siriv nimazi. Saawe tana, tileep imin livaa tau ipoop mako, ve azaawa ipuli. Aazne, ila uraat to Krisi, Maaron igham eval to nughmariŋ timin i natŋa. Yes Yuda, ve yes tau Yuda mako na paam. Yes tana ta timin Yerusalem to sambam natŋa.\f* \x * \xo 4:27 \xt Is 54:1\x*
\m 
\v 28 Yam toŋvetaz, yam amin Sara naatu Isak. Pasaa, saveeŋ mbuaaŋ to Maaron imin eez payam gha amin i tauu natŋa. \x * \xo 4:28 \xt Ro 9:8\x*
\m 
\v 29 Ve matamim iŋgal imuul ila pa ŋgar tau muuŋ Ismael igham pa Isak na. Ŋeer tau ivot itaghon eez to iit tamtamon to taan na, ighur pataŋani pa taazi tau ivot ila Maaron Avuvu tapiri. Aazne, ŋgar raraate ivotvot. Pasaa, yes tau titaghon eez to tutuuŋ na, tighurghur pataŋani pa iit tau Maaron Avuvu igham ghiit tamin i tauu natŋa na. \x * \xo 4:29 \xt Gnp 21:9; Ga 5:11, 6:12\x*
\m 
\v 30 Ve Maaron aliiŋa tau tiboode na isaav mindai? Isaav tauvene ighe:
\q2 “Uziir besooŋa livaa yesuru naatu tighau! Pa besooŋa livaa naatu irau ileep tomania livaa tau ruum tauu na naatu, ve yesuru tiyooz pa gabua to tamazi ne mako.” \x * \xo 4:30 \xt Gnp 21:10; Yo 8:35\x*
\m 
\v 31 Tauvene yam toŋvetaz, alooŋ. Iit besooŋa livaa natŋa mako. Iit tinaan, i ruum tauu. \x * \xo 4:31 \xt Ga 3:29, 5:1, 13\x*
\c 5
\s1 Tamtamon to Krisi timin besooŋa pa tutuuŋ mako
\p 
\v 1 Tauvene iit tamin besooŋa pa tutuuŋ muul mako. Pasaa, Krisi ipas ghiit pa eez to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ wa. Tauvene ayooz ariaaŋ. Apul tamtamon tigham gham amin besooŋa muul sov. \x * \xo 5:1 \xt Yo 8:36; Ro 7:6, 8:2+; Ga 5:13\x*
\p 
\v 2 Alooŋ. Yau Paulus nasaav ghazooŋa payam tauvene: Isaav ighe alooŋ zeran tawe aliŋazi, ve tirav waromim leso aduduuŋ ila Maaron maata, ene pale uraat to Krisi irau iuul gham mako. Mako kat.
\v 3 Yau nasaav ghazooŋa payam muul. Yam asov tau aghe ataghon eez to tutuuŋ ve ayok pa tirav waromim na, yam aat ataghon tutuuŋ ta naol ne le isov, o aduduuŋ ila Maaron maata. \x * \xo 5:3 \xt Ro 2:25; Ga 3:10\x*
\m 
\v 4 Tauvene yam tau anumeer ŋgar to taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ to igham gham aduduuŋ ila Maaron maata na, ayamaan gham. Pa ene yam arav motin taumim pa Krisi ve apul poia to Maaron wa. \x * \xo 5:4 \xt Ga 2:21\x*
\p 
\v 5 Eemon iit tau taghur ila to Krisi ne, Maaron Avuvu ipapalot ghiit ve tasasaŋan saawe to Maaron itotoi ghiit ighe iit taduduuŋ ila i maata. Gabua tawe, tauta taghurghur mataan pani kat. \x * \xo 5:5 \xt Ro 8:23+; 2Tim 4:8\x*
\m 
\v 6 Iit tau taleep ila to Yesu Krisi na, tagham ŋgar tiina pa ravuuŋ tamtamon warozi muul mako. Pa ighe tirav waroon, ma tiravu mako, ene gabua to uliin mon. Ve isaav ighe ghuruuŋ ila toit ipaburigin ghiit gha loloon pa tamtamon ve tagham poghani zi, ene gabua tauu. \x * \xo 5:6 \xt 1Kor 7:19; Ga 6:15; Kol 3:11\x*
\p 
\v 7-8 Muuŋ, yam alaan duduuŋ itaghon eez to saveeŋ onoon. Aazne, sei iponpoon gham pa landooŋ tsiam? Saveeŋ ŋgoreeŋ toozi tau ikau ŋgar tsiam na, ene ilam pa Maaron tau ipoi gham amin le ne mako. \x * \xo 5:7-8 \xt 1Kor 9:24; Ga 1:6, 3:1\x*
\m 
\v 9 Tauvene ayamaan gham. “Pa yis ŋgiira mon, ene irau ipasaria palawa tiina.” \x * \xo 5:9 \xt 1Kor 5:6\x*
\m 
\v 10 Eemon yau naghur ila to Maaron naghe i tauu pale ipaduduuŋ gham leso ataghon ŋgar tooni imin yau. Yau nakankaan pa sei tau ikau ŋgar tsiam. Eemon ŋeer tawe pale igham atuya to sosor tooni tana. \x * \xo 5:10 \xt Ga 1:7\x*
\p 
\v 11 Yam toŋvetaz, yau nawatagh. Zeran siriv tiŋgalŋgal saveeŋ karom payau tighe yau taug navovotia saveeŋ pa tamtamon naghe yes aat titaghon tutuuŋ to Mose, ve tirav warozi, o poia. Laak, ighe saveeŋ toozi tawe onoon, puughu mindai ta yes Yuda tighurghur pataŋani payau soone? Imin ta naghamgham tauvene, kanaŋ saveeŋ tau navovotia pa mateegh to Yesu izala ai pambarooŋ na, irau ireu tamtamon lolozi muul mako. \x * \xo 5:11 \xt 1Kor 1:23; Ga 6:12\x*
\m 
\v 12 Yes tau tikau ŋgar tsiam ve tiyaryaaŋ pa ravuuŋ waromim na, yau naghe tipaal tauzi lambezi paam, o poia!
\s1 Ŋgar to loloon muŋgaana ve ŋgar tau Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ loolo pani na tipaparav
\p 
\v 13 Yam toŋvetaz, Maaron ipoi gham amin i le, leso amin besooŋa pa tutuuŋ muul sov. Eemon ŋgar tana imin puughu payam to ataghon ŋgar to lolomim muŋgaana sov. Yam aat lolomim pa taumim, ve avaule gham. \x * \xo 5:13 \xt 1Kor 8:9; 1Pe 2:16\x*
\m 
\v 14 Pa tutuuŋ tisov tigheen ila tutuuŋ eemon loolo, ene vene: “Lolom pa tamtamon ve ugham poghani zi, imin yo lolom pa taum.” \x * \xo 5:14 \xt Mt 22:37+; Ro 13:8+; Yems 2:8\x*
\p 
\v 15 Eemon isaav ighe yam avazorai gham ve avomim ivaghani gham imin ŋgavuun sagsag tau tiparav ve tivaghani zi, na ayamaan gham. Pa ighe anoknoki tauvene, ene pale avaghamun taumim le asaghat kat.
\p 
\v 16 Tauvene yau nasaav payam: Laghooŋ tsiam, yam aat ataghon ŋgar to Maaron Avuvu. Ighe agham tauvene, ene irau ataghon lolomim muŋgaana muul mako. \x * \xo 5:16 \xt Ro 8:4, 13:14; 1Pe 2:11\x*
\m 
\v 17 Aghita. Saawe isov, ŋgar to loloon muŋgaana ve Maaron Avuvu tivaghuru koi pa tauzi ve tipaparav. Pasaa, ŋgar tau Maaron Avuvu loolo pani na, ene loloon muŋgaana izorzoora. Ve ŋgar tau loloon muŋgaana iyaryaaŋ pani ne, ene paam Maaron Avuvu izorzoora. Tauta saa ŋgar tau aghe aghamu, ene irau aghamu mako. \x * \xo 5:17 \xt Ro 7:15, 8:6+\x*
\m 
\v 18 Eemon isaav ighe ataghon pooz to Maaron Avuvu, ene aat aleep ila tutuuŋ saamba muul mako. \x * \xo 5:18 \xt Ro 6:14, 8:2, 14\x*
\s1 Ŋgar to loloon muŋgaana
\p 
\v 19 Ŋgar tau loloon muŋgaana ipapazaagh ghiit pani ne, ene iit tawataghi wa. Ene ŋgar tauvene: Taghur boog, tagham ŋgar tau ŋgalaaŋa mako, loloon ipazaagh ghiit pa ŋgar sasaghati ve tala pa naghoon mon, \x * \xo 5:19 \xt Ro 13:13+; Ep 5:3+\x*
\m 
\v 20 tabees pa maaron karomŋa, ŋgar to ghamuuŋ mur, taghur koi pa tamtamon, tavazorai ghiit, taghita zetaanŋa tau lezi gabua katini na ve ireu loloon, ateen tuuku, takokook, mataan iŋgalŋgal tauun mon, tavarewai ghiit ve taleep soghan soghan, tagham ŋgar taghe lupuuŋ toit mon ta iduduuŋ kat ila Maaron maata,
\v 21 taghur koi pa zetaanŋa tau lezi gabua katini, taghun le tavaghamgham, itiŋa zetaanŋa talup ghiit ve tagham ŋgar sasaghati naol toman oroor tiina, ve ŋgar sasaghati siriv paam. Saveeŋ tau muuŋ nasavia payam, tauta aazne nayoli muul: Zeran tau titaghon ŋgar tauvene, yes irau tigham lepoogh poia izi Maaron nugh tooni mako. Pasaa, yes titaghon pooz tooni mako. \x * \xo 5:21 \xt 1Kor 6:9; Syg 22:15\x*
\s1 Ŋgar tau Maaron Avuvu ipapaburigin ghiit pani
\p 
\v 22 Ve Maaron Avuvu ipapaburigin ghiit pa ghamuuŋ ŋgar tauvene: Loloon pa tamtamon ve tagham poghani zi, loloon poia kat irau saawe, tatotoi ŋgar luuma pa tamtamon ve itiŋa tavalupu ghiit tamin eemon, tatatan ateen, tagham poghania tamtamon ve tatotoi ŋgar popoia mon pazi, mataan iŋgal saveeŋ mbuaaŋ toit ve tataghoni, \x * \xo 5:22 \xt Ep 5:9; Kol 3:12\x*
\m 
\v 23 ŋgar marowa, ve taŋgin tauun poi. Aghita. Ŋgar tauvene, ene iduduuŋ mon. Tutuuŋ eta iŋgalsekin ghiit pani mako. \x * \xo 5:23 \xt Ro 3:31; 1Tim 1:9\x*
\m 
\v 24 Yes tau timin Yesu Krisi le na, tigham lolozi muŋgaana tomania ŋgar sasaghati naol tau lolozi muŋgaana tawe ipapaghaar zi pani na, ve tiravu izala ai pambarooŋ gha imaat wa. \x * \xo 5:24 \xt Ro 6:6; Ga 2:20; Kol 3:5\x*
\p 
\v 25 Iit tagham lepoogh paaghu ila to Maaron Avuvu wa. Tauvene laghooŋ toit, iit aat tataghon pooz to Maaron Avuvu. \x * \xo 5:25 \xt Ro 8:4, 12+\x*
\m 
\v 26 Tauvene tapait tauun sov. Ve tawat zetaanŋa, ma taghur koi pa yes tau lezi gabua katini na sov. \x * \xo 5:26 \xt Ro 12:10+; Pil 2:3\x*
\c 6
\s1 Tatotoi ŋgar poia pa tamtamon itaghon ŋgar to Krisi
\p 
\v 1 Yam toŋvetaz, isaav ighe tsiam eta itap ve igham sosor, na yam tau ataghon ŋgar to Maaron Avuvu na, ala apaduduuŋa toman saveeŋ marowa, leso itoor ŋgar tooni imuul ila pa Krisi. Eemon ayamaan gham. Pa aat tovaaŋ ivot payam paam. \x * \xo 6:1 \xt Mt 18:15; 2Tim 2:25; Yems 5:19\x*
\m 
\v 2 Avaule gham pa badooŋ pataŋani tsiam. Leso atotoi tutuuŋ to Krisi anooŋa ivot. \x * \xo 6:2 \xt Yo 13:34; Ro 15:1; 1Tes 5:14\x*
\p 
\v 3 Isaav ighe ŋeer eta ighe i iliiv zeetŋa, ene itombaan tauu. Pasaa, tamtamon tauvene, i igham ŋgar irao soone. \x * \xo 6:3 \xt Ro 12:3; 1Kor 3:18, 8:2\x*
\m 
\v 4 Tauvene tamtamon eŋaeŋa irau tigabiiz poghania uraat to tauzi: Uraat toozi poia ila Maaron maata, ma mako? Ighe uraat toozi poia, ene yes irau tipakur zi pani. Ve tigabiiz uraat toozi tomania uraat to zetazŋa sov.
\v 5 Pasaa, iit eŋaeŋa aat tabaad pataŋani toit toit. \x * \xo 6:5 \xt Ro 14:12\x*
\s1 Saa ŋgar tau ighe taghamu, ene pale murei tagham anooŋa tooni
\p 
\v 6 Isaav ighe tamtamon eta ipaghazoŋai gham pa Maaron aliiŋa, yam aat arei gabua tsiam popoia siriv pani paam. \x * \xo 6:6 \xt 1Kor 9:7, 11, 14\x*
\p 
\v 7 Ayamaan taumim. Irau atombaan Maaron mako. Saa aniiŋ tau ighe tavazoghi, ene aniiŋ tana mon ta pale izaa ve tataii. \x * \xo 6:7 \xt Ro 2:6; 1Kor 6:9; 2Kor 9:6\x*
\m 
\v 8 Tamtamon tau ighe ivazogh gabua tau ipazaagh loolo muŋgaana, ene aat ighita anooŋa tauvene: I pale isaghat ve ilale. Ve tamtamon tau ighe ivazogh gabua tau ipariaaŋ ŋgar to Maaron Avuvu ila loolo, ene aat ighita anooŋa poia tauvene: I pale igham lepoogh poia ila to Maaron Avuvu taghon taghon gha ila. \x * \xo 6:8 \xt Ro 8:13\x*
\p 
\v 9 Tiniin imum pa ghamuuŋ ŋgar popoia sov. Pa ighe tapuli mako, ve tanoknok ghamuuŋni, ene aat taghita anooŋa ila saawe tooni. \x * \xo 6:9 \xt 1Kor 15:58; 2Tes 3:13; Hib 10:36\x*
\m 
\v 10 Tauvene isaav ighe iit irau tauul tamtamon eta, na tauule. Tagham poghania tamtamon tisov. Ve yes tau tighur ila to Krisi na, iit aat tagham poghani zi kat. Pasaa, yes timin toŋvetaz toit. \x * \xo 6:10 \xt Ep 2:19; 1Tes 5:15; 1Tim 6:18; 2Pe 1:7\x*
\s1 Mateegh to Krisi izala ai pambarooŋ, ene gabua tauu
\p 
\v 11 Aghita bodeeŋ tintiina tau taug nimag nabood zi ne.
\v 12 Yes tau timburmbuur gham pa taghoniiŋ tutuuŋ ve ravuuŋ waromim na, ene tigham pa ezazi mon. Ve tiroi paam: Isaav ighe tivotia saveeŋ pa mateegh to Krisi izala ai pambarooŋ, ene pale yes tau tighur ila mako na tighur pataŋani pazi. \x * \xo 6:12 \xt Ga 5:11; Pil 3:18\x*
\m 
\v 13 Yes tau tiyooz ariaaŋ pa ŋgar to ravuuŋ tamtamon warozi na, tauzi titaghon duduŋai tutuuŋ to Mose mako. Yes tizoornugh tighe tirav waromim pasaa, tighe tigham gham ataghon ŋgar toozi. Leso tipait tauzi ezazi.
\p 
\v 14 Eemon yau irau napait taug ezag, ma tamtamon ite paam eeza ne mako. Yesu Krisi tau imaat izala ai pambarooŋ, i mon ta igham ghau tintinig ve napait eeza. Yau naghita naghe saawe tau tirav Krisi imaat izala ai pambarooŋ, tirav ghau namaat tomania. Tauta mateegh tooni tapiri irav matin ŋgar to taan tau muuŋ igheen ila lolog na gha imaat wa. \x * \xo 6:14 \xt Ro 6:6; 1Kor 1:31, 2:2; Pil 3:7+\x*
\m 
\v 15 Tauvene isaav ighe tirav waroon, ma mako, ene gabua sorok. Uraat to Maaron tau igham ghiit tamin paaghu, tane mon ta gabua tauu. \x * \xo 6:15 \xt Yo 3:3; Ro 2:28; 2Kor 5:17; Ga 5:6\x*
\m 
\v 16 Tamtamon tisov tau titaghon eez tauvene, Maaron tauu pale loolo isaghatin zi, ve ighur luuma tooni izaa toozi. Pasaa, yes ta timin Israela duduuŋ.
\p 
\v 17 Aiyo, yau naghe napasov saveeŋ tsiau. Aazne ve ila, lolog pa tamtamon eta ighur pataŋani payau muul mako. Pa sip tau ighenaar ila tinig ne, ene nagham zi pa Yesu Krisi eeza. \x * \xo 6:17 \xt 2Kor 4:10, 11:23\x*
\p 
\v 18 Yam toŋvetaz, poia to Tiina toit Yesu Krisi igheen tomani gham. Onoon. 
